(101, 'nl', '<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Geen bezwaarcertificaat</h3>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>Datum: {date}</p>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>Aan wie het ook aangaat</p>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>Dit certificaat is bedoeld om aanspraak te maken op een Geen Bezwaarcertificaat (NoC) voor mevrouw/dhr. {employee_name} als zij/hij lid wordt en haar/zijn diensten verleent aan een andere organisatie. Het wordt ge&iuml;nformeerd als zij/hij al haar/zijn saldos heeft gewist en haar/zijn zekerheid heeft ontvangen van {app_name} Company.</p>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>We wensen haar/hem veel succes in de toekomst.</p>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>Eerlijk,</p>\n            \n            <p>{employee_name}</p>\n            \n            <p>{designation}</p>\n            \n            <p>Handtekening</p>\n            \n            <p>{app_name}</p>', 17, '2022-12-03 10:08:05', '2022-12-03 10:08:05'),
(102, 'pl', '<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Certyfikat braku sprzeciwu</h3>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>Data: {date}</p>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>Do kogo to mo탉e dotyczy</p>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>Ten certyfikat su탉y do ubiegania si o Certyfikat No Objection Certificate (NoC) dla Pani/Pana {employee_name}, jeli ona/ona docza i wiadczy swoje usugi na rzecz jakiejkolwiek innej organizacji. Jest o tym informowany, poniewa탉 wyczyci wszystkie swoje salda i otrzyma swoje zabezpieczenie od firmy {app_name}.</p>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>탈yczymy jej/jej powodzenia w przyszoci.</p>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>Z powa탉aniem,</p>\n            \n            <p>{employee_name}</p>\n            \n            <p>{designation}</p>\n            \n            <p>Podpis</p>\n            \n            <p>{app_name}</p>', 17, '2022-12-03 10:08:05', '2022-12-03 10:08:05'),
(103, 'pt', '<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Certificado de n&atilde;o obje&ccedil;&atilde;o</h3>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>Data: {date}</p>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>A quem interessar</p>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>Este certificado &eacute; para reivindicar um Certificado de N&atilde;o Obje&ccedil;&atilde;o (NoC) para a Sra. / Sr. {employee_name} se ela ingressar e fornecer seus servi&ccedil;os a qualquer outra organiza&ccedil;&atilde;o. &Eacute; informado que ela cancelou todos os seus saldos e recebeu sua garantia da empresa {app_name}.</p>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>Desejamos-lhe boa sorte no futuro.</p>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>Sinceramente,</p>\n            \n            <p>{employee_name}</p>\n            \n            <p>{designation}</p>\n            \n            <p>Assinatura</p>\n            \n            <p>{app_name}</p>', 17, '2022-12-03 10:08:05', '2022-12-03 10:08:05'),
(104, 'ru', '<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">鬼筠龜龜克逵 棘閨 棘勻龜龜 勻棘鈞逵菌筠戟龜橘</h3>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>逵逵: {date}</p>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>棘均棘 閨 棘 戟龜 克逵逵剋棘</p>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>葵棘 筠龜龜克逵 極筠畇戟逵鈞戟逵筠戟 畇剋 極棘剋筠戟龜 鬼筠龜龜克逵逵 棘閨 棘勻龜龜 勻棘鈞逵菌筠戟龜橘 (NoC) 畇剋 均-菌龜 / 均-戟逵 {employee_name}, 筠剋龜 棘戟逵 / 棘戟 極龜棘筠畇龜戟筠 龜 極筠畇棘逵勻剋筠 勻棘龜 剋均龜 剋閨棘橘 畇均棘橘 棘均逵戟龜鈞逵龜龜. 鬼棘棘閨逵筠, 棘 棘戟逵/棘戟 棘龜龜剋逵 勻筠 勻棘龜 閨逵剋逵戟 龜 極棘剋龜剋逵 勻棘 閨筠鈞棘極逵戟棘 棘 克棘劇極逵戟龜龜 {app_name}.</p>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p> 菌筠剋逵筠劇 筠橘/筠劇 畇逵龜 勻 閨畇筠劇.</p>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>克筠戟戟筠,</p>\n            \n            <p>{employee_name}</p>\n            \n            <p>{designation}</p>\n            \n            <p>棘畇極龜</p>\n            \n            <p>{app_name}</p>', 17, '2022-12-03 10:08:05', '2022-12-03 10:08:05'),
(105, 'ar', '<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">娩碼膜馬 晩膜 碼晩馬</h3>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>碼魔碼邈漠: {date}</p>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>瑪   碼粒邈</p>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>莫 碼娩碼膜馬 漠巒巒馬 慢碼磨馬 磨娩碼膜馬 晩膜 碼晩馬 (NoC) 卍膜馬 / 碼卍膜 {employee_name} 瑪莫碼 碼彎魔 瑪 粒 摩卍卍馬 粒漠邈 膜魔 漠膜碼魔碼 / 漠膜碼魔碼. 魔 瑪磨碼曼 粒 碼 磨魔巒馬 寞晩 粒邈巒膜魔 碼卍魔碼 粒碼  娩邈馬 {app_name}.</p>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>魔 碼 / 碼 碼魔  碼卍魔磨.</p>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>磨瑪漠碼巒</p>\n            \n            <p>{employee_name}</p>\n            \n            <p>{designation}</p>\n            \n            <p>碼魔晩</p>\n            \n            <p>{app_name}</p>', 18, '2022-12-03 21:07:22', '2022-12-03 21:07:22'),
(106, 'da', '<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Ingen indsigelsesattest</h3>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>Dato: {date}</p>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>Til hvem det m&aring;tte vedr&oslash;re</p>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>Dette certifikat er for at g&oslash;re krav p&aring; et No Objection Certificate (NoC) for Ms. / Mr. {employee_name}, hvis hun/han tilslutter sig og leverer sine tjenester til enhver anden organisation. Det informeres, da hun/han har udlignet alle sine saldi og modtaget sin sikkerhed fra {app_name}-virksomheden.</p>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>Vi &oslash;nsker hende/ham held og lykke i fremtiden.</p>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>Med venlig hilsen</p>\n            \n            <p>{employee_name}</p>\n            \n            <p>{designation}</p>\n            \n            <p>Underskrift</p>\n            \n            <p>{app_name}</p>', 18, '2022-12-03 21:07:22', '2022-12-03 21:07:22'),
(107, 'de', '<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Kein Einwand-Zertifikat</h3>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>Datum {date}</p>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>Wen auch immer es betrifft</p>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>Dieses Zertifikat soll ein Unbedenklichkeitszertifikat (NoC) f&uuml;r Frau / Herrn {employee_name} beanspruchen, wenn sie/er einer anderen Organisation beitritt und ihre/seine Dienste anbietet. Sie wird informiert, da sie/er alle ihre/seine Guthaben ausgeglichen und ihre/seine Sicherheit von der Firma {app_name} erhalten hat.</p>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>Wir w&uuml;nschen ihr/ihm viel Gl&uuml;ck f&uuml;r die Zukunft.</p>\n            \n            \n            \n            <p>Aufrichtig,</p>\n            \n            <p>{employee_name}</p>\n            \n            <p>{designation}</p>\n            \n            <p>Unterschrift</p>\n            \n            <p>{app_name}</p>', 18, '2022-12-03 21:07:22', '2022-12-03 21:07:22'),
(108, 'en', '<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18pt;\"><strong>No Objection Certificate</strong></span></p>\n            \n            <p>Date: {date}</p>\n            \n            <p>To Whomsoever It May Concern</p>\n            \n            <p>This certificate is to claim a No Objection Certificate (NoC) for Ms. / Mr. {employee_name} if she/he joins and provides her/his services to any other organization. It is informed as she/he has cleared all her/his balances and received her/his security from {app_name} Company.</p>\n            \n            <p>We wish her/him good luck in the future.</p>\n            \n            <p>Sincerely,</p>\n            <p>{employee_name}</p>\n            <p>{designation}</p>\n            <p>Signature</p>\n            <p>{app_name}</p>', 18, '2022-12-03 21:07:22', '2022-12-03 21:07:22'),
